<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirmation de votre commande</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #18181b; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .header { background: #18181b; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #facc15; letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .header .logo span { color: #ffffff; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52525b; margin: 0 0 20px; }
    .summary { border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .summary-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f4f4f5; font-size: 14px; }
    .summary-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .summary-row .label { color: #71717a; }
    .summary-row .value { font-weight: 600; color: #18181b; }
    .total-row { background: #f4f4f5; }
    .total-row .value { font-size: 16px; color: #18181b; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #dcfce7; color: #15803d; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .footer { background: #f4f4f5; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #a1a1aa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo"><span>Lvl</span>Up</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h1>Commande confirmée <span class="badge">Confirmée</span></h1>
      <p>Bonjour {{ profile.firstName }},</p>
      <p>Nous avons bien enregistré votre commande. Voici le récapitulatif :</p>
      <div class="summary">
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Référence commande</span>
          <span class="value">{{ order.id|slice(0, 8)|upper }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Profil</span>
          <span class="value">{{ profile.firstName }} {{ profile.lastName }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if order.packageType %}
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Formule</span>
          <span class="value">{{ order.packageType }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Statut</span>
          <span class="value">{{ order.status.value }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Montant réglé</span>
          <span class="value">{{ (order.paidAmount / 100)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row total-row">
          <span class="label"><strong>Total commande</strong></span>
          <span class="value">{{ (order.totalAmount / 100)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Vous pouvez consulter le détail de votre commande directement depuis votre espace personnel.</p>
      <p>Pour toute question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.</p>
      <p>À bientôt sur LvlUp !</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} LvlUp &mdash; Tous droits réservés.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
